text: The 2005 Wagner Seahawks football team represented Wagner College in the 2005 NCAA Division I-AA football season as a member of the Northeast Conference (NEC). The Seahawks were led by 25th-year head coach Walt Hameline and played their home games at Wagner College Stadium. Wagner finished the season 6–5 overall and 3–4 in NEC play to place in a three-way tie for third. ==Schedule== ==References== Wagner Category:Wagner Seahawks football seasons Wagner Seahawks football
